						<div class="postbody">The if statement thing you were asking about goes like this:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; lda shooting<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; cmp #1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; bne skip_shooting_down<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda #0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta shooting<br />skip_shooting_down:</div><br /><br />For an if-then-else, you would do it more like this:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; lda shooting<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; cmp #1<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; bne else_clause<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; DO STUFF<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; jmp end_else<br />else_clause:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; DO OTHER STUFF<br />end_else:</div></div>

